        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Product Requirements Document \u2014 Behind Paywall"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "level": 2,
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Problem Statement"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Content creators with loyal audiences are leaving significant revenue on the table because they rely entirely on free content with no monetization infrastructure. Behind Paywall is a platform + methodology that helps creators launch, grow, and scale paid subscription tiers \u2014 turning their best content and expertise into predictable monthly recurring revenue. It addresses both the strategy (what to put behind a paywall, how to price it) and the execution (platform setup, subscriber acquisition, retention)."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "level": 2,
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Goals"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "unordered-list",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "list-item",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Help creators launch a paid subscription tier within 14 days of joining"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "list-item",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Provide AI-assisted content strategy for what goes free vs. what goes paid"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "list-item",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Build the systems and email sequences that convert free readers to paid subscribers"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "list-item",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Target: creator goes from $0 to $5K/month in subscription revenue within 90 days"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "level": 2,
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Core Features"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "unordered-list",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "list-item",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Paywall Strategy Builder: AI analyzes creator's content library and recommends paywall structure"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "list-item",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Subscriber Acquisition Playbook: content calendar designed to funnel free readers to paid"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "list-item",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Email Conversion Sequences: pre-written, customizable upgrade sequences"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "list-item",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Churn Prevention System: identifies at-risk subscribers and triggers re-engagement flows"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "list-item",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Revenue Dashboard: MRR, churn, LTV, and content engagement by subscriber tier"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
  }
